byline.original: By YAMICHE ALCINDOR and AMY CHOZICK

abstract: Some of biggest hip-hop stars in country, including Beyonce and Jay Z, campaign with Hillary Clinton in Cleveland, part of bid to boost turnout among young black voters.

headline.print_headline: Hip-Hop Stars Align for a Clinton Rally
headline.main: A Hip-Hop Political Rally, Starring Beyoncé, Jay Z (and Hillary Clinton)

snippet: To the cheers of thousands, top artists headlined a Cleveland event to urge millennial and African-American voters to go to the polls on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: To the cheers of thousands, top artists headlined a Cleveland event to urge millennial and African-American voters to go to the polls on Tuesday.
